claim.claim-text:
A system, comprising:
an electrical enclosure (10);
a first electrical unit (12) removably disposed within the electrical enclosure (10), wherein the first electrical unit comprises a first surface opposite to a second surface;
a first electrical module (14) removably disposed within the first electrical unit (12), wherein the first electrical module (14) is inserted into the first electrical unit (12) in a first direction (36) from the first surface to the second surface;
a first heat spreader (76) coupled to the first electrical module (14) within the first electrical unit (12), wherein the first heat spreader (76) comprises a first tapered coupling (100);
a heat sink (44) comprising a second tapered coupling (102), wherein the heat sink (44) is parallel to the second surface of the first electrical unit (12), and the second tapered coupling (102) is configured to operatively couple with the first tapered coupling (100) of the first heat spreader (76) to form a physical thermal connection that facilitates heat transfer between the first electrical module (14) and the heat sink (44).
